{
  "video_id": "dkmpRQdJslI",
  "title": "When workers own companies, the economy is more resilient | Niki Okuk",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12689.0,
      "end_time": 14200.0,
      "text": "Are you tired of your boss?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14893.0,
      "end_time": 16249.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16273.0,
      "end_time": 18114.0,
      "text": "Are you tired of going to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18138.0,
      "end_time": 20571.0,
      "text": "and making money for other people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21785.0,
      "end_time": 23361.0,
      "text": "And who are those people anyways?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23385.0,
      "end_time": 25464.0,
      "text": "Those people that make money from your work."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26198.0,
      "end_time": 28960.0,
      "text": "Well, they&#39;re capitalists."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28120.0,
      "end_time": 29396.0,
      "text": "They have capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29420.0,
      "end_time": 32870.0,
      "text": "and they use your labor to make more capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32793.0,
      "end_time": 34867.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re tired of going to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34891.0,
      "end_time": 37960.0,
      "text": "and making money for other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37120.0,
      "end_time": 38788.0,
      "text": "then you&#39;re probably like me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38812.0,
      "end_time": 40579.0,
      "text": "just tired of capitalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41621.0,
      "end_time": 44643.0,
      "text": "Which is ironic, because I&#39;m a capitalist."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44667.0,
      "end_time": 46850.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46109.0,
      "end_time": 47832.0,
      "text": "I own a small business --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47856.0,
      "end_time": 50380.0,
      "text": "Rco Tires in Compton."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 50404.0,
      "end_time": 52367.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, when I read Van Jones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52391.0,
      "end_time": 55309.0,
      "text": "and he wrote, \"Let&#39;s make green collar jobs in the hood,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55333.0,
      "end_time": 57376.0,
      "text": "I took him really seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57908.0,
      "end_time": 61608.0,
      "text": "So I cofounded, own and operate a tire recycling company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61632.0,
      "end_time": 63594.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m really proud of what we&#39;ve done."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63618.0,
      "end_time": 66991.0,
      "text": "So far, we&#39;ve recycled a hundred million pounds of rubber."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67402.0,
      "end_time": 71427.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 21 million gallons of oil diverted from landfills"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71451.0,
      "end_time": 72615.0,
      "text": "into new products."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73550.0,
      "end_time": 74205.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 74229.0,
      "end_time": 75878.0,
      "text": "We also employ about 15 guys --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76468.0,
      "end_time": 78170.0,
      "text": "mostly people of color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78410.0,
      "end_time": 79411.0,
      "text": "most of whom are felons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79435.0,
      "end_time": 81310.0,
      "text": "and we pay above the minimum wage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81334.0,
      "end_time": 84276.0,
      "text": "and we are now proud members of the United Steelworkers Union."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84768.0,
      "end_time": 90327.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90351.0,
      "end_time": 92890.0,
      "text": "Now, Rco is not a cooperative now."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92914.0,
      "end_time": 96581.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a privately held company with community-minded ownership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96605.0,
      "end_time": 98359.0,
      "text": "but I would like it to become one."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98383.0,
      "end_time": 100678.0,
      "text": "I would like for them to fire the boss --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100702.0,
      "end_time": 102410.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s me."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102650.0,
      "end_time": 103113.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103137.0,
      "end_time": 104583.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to tell you why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104607.0,
      "end_time": 106929.0,
      "text": "but first, let me tell you how we got started."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107683.0,
      "end_time": 108833.0,
      "text": "So a lot of people ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108857.0,
      "end_time": 110291.0,
      "text": "\"How did Rco come to be?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 110315.0,
      "end_time": 111853.0,
      "text": "And I have to be really honest."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112239.0,
      "end_time": 114244.0,
      "text": "I leveraged my white privilege."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114584.0,
      "end_time": 118237.0,
      "text": "So, here&#39;s how white privilege worked for me and Rco."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119268.0,
      "end_time": 123113.0,
      "text": "My white grandmother was born on her family&#39;s plantation"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123137.0,
      "end_time": 125791.0,
      "text": "in Arkansas in 1918."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125815.0,
      "end_time": 128745.0,
      "text": "She traveled with her white father west,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128769.0,
      "end_time": 130338.0,
      "text": "following the oil boom."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130362.0,
      "end_time": 133542.0,
      "text": "And he held various union oil jobs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133566.0,
      "end_time": 137270.0,
      "text": "jobs which would have never been given to my black great-grandfather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137510.0,
      "end_time": 138581.0,
      "text": "had he lived here at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139562.0,
      "end_time": 141491.0,
      "text": "Granny became a hairdresser"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141515.0,
      "end_time": 145420.0,
      "text": "and then got a loan with her husband"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145444.0,
      "end_time": 147513.0,
      "text": "who built their home in West Los Angeles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147538.0,
      "end_time": 151160.0,
      "text": "a loan which would never have been given to a black family at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152241.0,
      "end_time": 154770.0,
      "text": "And after my grandfather passed away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 154101.0,
      "end_time": 155880.0,
      "text": "my granny was able to keep that house"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155904.0,
      "end_time": 158581.0,
      "text": "because she had his pension and his health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158605.0,
      "end_time": 160373.0,
      "text": "from a state job which he held,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160397.0,
      "end_time": 163190.0,
      "text": "which again, would have never been given to a black man"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 163430.0,
      "end_time": 165429.0,
      "text": "before the anti-discrimination act of the 1960s."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165868.0,
      "end_time": 167726.0,
      "text": "So, you fast-forward 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167750.0,
      "end_time": 169138.0,
      "text": "and I graduate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169162.0,
      "end_time": 170864.0,
      "text": "and I want to start my own business"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 170888.0,
      "end_time": 172765.0,
      "text": "with a pile of debt and a credit card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172789.0,
      "end_time": 175131.0,
      "text": "and no experience in the tire industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175156.0,
      "end_time": 177393.0,
      "text": "But I had what most people didn&#39;t have."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177417.0,
      "end_time": 181896.0,
      "text": "I had a clean, safe, free place to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182856.0,
      "end_time": 184603.0,
      "text": "I moved in with my grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184628.0,
      "end_time": 186952.0,
      "text": "and I was able to rent our first warehouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186977.0,
      "end_time": 188153.0,
      "text": "buy our first truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188177.0,
      "end_time": 189737.0,
      "text": "pay our first employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189761.0,
      "end_time": 192174.0,
      "text": "because I didn&#39;t have to worry about paying myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192199.0,
      "end_time": 193982.0,
      "text": "because I didn&#39;t need to feed myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 194600.0,
      "end_time": 197547.0,
      "text": "because I am the direct beneficiary of generations of white privilege."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198523.0,
      "end_time": 202587.0,
      "text": "Now, telling the story of white privilege is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 202611.0,
      "end_time": 204400.0,
      "text": "because very often people say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204640.0,
      "end_time": 205922.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, we want more companies like yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 205946.0,
      "end_time": 207103.0,
      "text": "We want more Rco&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 207128.0,
      "end_time": 208976.0,
      "text": "we want more black-owned businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 209100.0,
      "end_time": 211665.0,
      "text": "female-led, triple bottom line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 211689.0,
      "end_time": 212861.0,
      "text": "Ban the Box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 212885.0,
      "end_time": 214846.0,
      "text": "green manufacturing companies,\" right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 215559.0,
      "end_time": 218202.0,
      "text": "But the question we have to ask is, where is the wealth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 218226.0,
      "end_time": 219377.0,
      "text": "Where is the money?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219401.0,
      "end_time": 221267.0,
      "text": "Where&#39;s the capital in our communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221291.0,
      "end_time": 223450.0,
      "text": "to build the types of businesses that we want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223474.0,
      "end_time": 226220.0,
      "text": "And in telling a story of the white side of my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 226460.0,
      "end_time": 227197.0,
      "text": "I needed a dozen ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 227221.0,
      "end_time": 229282.0,
      "text": "where blacks were excluded from the economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 229306.0,
      "end_time": 232854.0,
      "text": "whereas the white side of my family was able to gain access and traction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 232878.0,
      "end_time": 234273.0,
      "text": "and build wealth ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235440.0,
      "end_time": 239654.0,
      "text": "Primarily because racism and capitalism are best homies, but --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 239678.0,
      "end_time": 241480.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 241504.0,
      "end_time": 243957.0,
      "text": "but what that means is that when we ask ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 243981.0,
      "end_time": 246442.0,
      "text": "\"Why are our communities broke?\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 246466.0,
      "end_time": 248672.0,
      "text": "Like, we&#39;re not just broke because we&#39;re broke;"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 248696.0,
      "end_time": 250310.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re broke for a reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 250550.0,
      "end_time": 252171.0,
      "text": "Historical context really does matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 253530.0,
      "end_time": 255681.0,
      "text": "But our history tells another story as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 255705.0,
      "end_time": 258393.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s this incredible book called \"Collective Courage,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 258416.0,
      "end_time": 261632.0,
      "text": "which is the story of how thousands of African Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 261656.0,
      "end_time": 264176.0,
      "text": "have been able to build businesses and schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 264201.0,
      "end_time": 266444.0,
      "text": "hospitals, farming cooperatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 266468.0,
      "end_time": 268185.0,
      "text": "banks, financial institutions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 268209.0,
      "end_time": 270821.0,
      "text": "entire communities and sovereign economies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 270845.0,
      "end_time": 272267.0,
      "text": "without a lot of capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 272857.0,
      "end_time": 274774.0,
      "text": "And they did it by working together"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 274798.0,
      "end_time": 277205.0,
      "text": "and leveraging their community assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277229.0,
      "end_time": 278681.0,
      "text": "and trusting each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 278705.0,
      "end_time": 280405.0,
      "text": "and putting solidarity first --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 280429.0,
      "end_time": 283227.0,
      "text": "not just profits by any means necessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 284201.0,
      "end_time": 287513.0,
      "text": "And they didn&#39;t have to wait around for celebrities and athletes"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 287537.0,
      "end_time": 289823.0,
      "text": "to bring their money back to the hood."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 289847.0,
      "end_time": 292100.0,
      "text": "However, if you are a celebrity or an athlete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 293419.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re listening to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 293443.0,
      "end_time": 295229.0,
      "text": "please feel free to bring your money."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 295253.0,
      "end_time": 296895.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 297851.0,
      "end_time": 300870.0,
      "text": "But they did it through cooperative economics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 300111.0,
      "end_time": 301262.0,
      "text": "because they knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 301286.0,
      "end_time": 304394.0,
      "text": "that capitalism was never going to finance black liberation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 304763.0,
      "end_time": 308789.0,
      "text": "So, there are so many great examples in this book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 308814.0,
      "end_time": 310913.0,
      "text": "and I suggest that everybody just read it"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 310937.0,
      "end_time": 313180.0,
      "text": "because it answers the question I asked earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 313204.0,
      "end_time": 315508.0,
      "text": "which was where are we going to get the wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 315532.0,
      "end_time": 317608.0,
      "text": "to build the types of business that we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 317632.0,
      "end_time": 320480.0,
      "text": "And the answer is going to have to be cooperative economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320504.0,
      "end_time": 323464.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of different versions of cooperativism."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 323488.0,
      "end_time": 325908.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m talking about today is worker ownership."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 326504.0,
      "end_time": 328513.0,
      "text": "You may not have heard of worker ownership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 328537.0,
      "end_time": 330147.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s been an incredible tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 330171.0,
      "end_time": 332252.0,
      "text": "for black economic liberation for a century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 332276.0,
      "end_time": 334685.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s also working all over the world right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 335348.0,
      "end_time": 337266.0,
      "text": "You may have heard of Black Wall Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 337290.0,
      "end_time": 338481.0,
      "text": "or maybe the Zapatistas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 338505.0,
      "end_time": 341551.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ll give you an example that&#39;s a little bit closer to home."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 341575.0,
      "end_time": 344920.0,
      "text": "Right now, today, in South Bronx,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 344116.0,
      "end_time": 347313.0,
      "text": "is the country&#39;s largest worker-owned company."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 347337.0,
      "end_time": 350600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called Cooperative Home Care Associates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 350300.0,
      "end_time": 352989.0,
      "text": "and it was founded by black and Latinx home care workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 353140.0,
      "end_time": 356870.0,
      "text": "who are now able to pay themselves living wages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 356111.0,
      "end_time": 357366.0,
      "text": "they have full-time hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 357390.0,
      "end_time": 359180.0,
      "text": "they have benefits and a pension,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 359420.0,
      "end_time": 361619.0,
      "text": "through their membership as a unit of SEIU."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 362598.0,
      "end_time": 366446.0,
      "text": "And these women owners now receive a dividend back on their ownership"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 366470.0,
      "end_time": 368763.0,
      "text": "every year that the company has been profitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 368787.0,
      "end_time": 370167.0,
      "text": "which has been most years."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 370809.0,
      "end_time": 374730.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re able to really enjoy the fruits of their labor"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 374754.0,
      "end_time": 376412.0,
      "text": "because they fired the boss."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 377119.0,
      "end_time": 378788.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have any big investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 378812.0,
      "end_time": 380420.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have fat-cat CEOs"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 380444.0,
      "end_time": 383500.0,
      "text": "or absentee owners taking the profit out of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 383957.0,
      "end_time": 387849.0,
      "text": "They each pay in about 1,000 dollars over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 387874.0,
      "end_time": 389790.0,
      "text": "in order to gain ownership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 389814.0,
      "end_time": 391163.0,
      "text": "and now they own their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 392418.0,
      "end_time": 395403.0,
      "text": "Now, there&#39;s hundreds of more examples of companies like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 395427.0,
      "end_time": 397261.0,
      "text": "springing up all across the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 397285.0,
      "end_time": 400534.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m so inspired by what they&#39;re doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 400558.0,
      "end_time": 403430.0,
      "text": "because it really represents an alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 403670.0,
      "end_time": 405980.0,
      "text": "to the type of economy we have now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 405122.0,
      "end_time": 406484.0,
      "text": "which exploits all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 407139.0,
      "end_time": 408790.0,
      "text": "It also represents an alternative"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 408814.0,
      "end_time": 412774.0,
      "text": "to waiting around for big investors to bring chain stores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 412798.0,
      "end_time": 414570.0,
      "text": "or big-box stores to our communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 414594.0,
      "end_time": 416870.0,
      "text": "because honestly, those types of developments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 416894.0,
      "end_time": 419218.0,
      "text": "they steal resources from our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 419242.0,
      "end_time": 422790.0,
      "text": "They put our mom-and-pop shops out of business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 422103.0,
      "end_time": 425199.0,
      "text": "they make our entrepreneurs into wage workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 425223.0,
      "end_time": 427290.0,
      "text": "and they take money out of our pocket"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 427530.0,
      "end_time": 428794.0,
      "text": "and send it to their shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 429851.0,
      "end_time": 433251.0,
      "text": "So, I was so inspired by all these stories of resistance and resilience"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 433275.0,
      "end_time": 436420.0,
      "text": "that I got together with a few people here in Los Angeles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 436670.0,
      "end_time": 437447.0,
      "text": "and we created LUCI."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 437815.0,
      "end_time": 441990.0,
      "text": "LUCI stands for the Los Angeles Union Cooperative Initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 442140.0,
      "end_time": 445110.0,
      "text": "and our objective is to create more worker-owned businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 445134.0,
      "end_time": 446800.0,
      "text": "here in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 446824.0,
      "end_time": 449182.0,
      "text": "So far, in the last year, we&#39;ve created two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 449206.0,
      "end_time": 451199.0,
      "text": "Pacific Electric, an electrical company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 451223.0,
      "end_time": 452778.0,
      "text": "and Vermont Gage Carwash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 452802.0,
      "end_time": 454565.0,
      "text": "which is right here in South-Central,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 454589.0,
      "end_time": 456621.0,
      "text": "some of you guys might be familiar with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 456645.0,
      "end_time": 461316.0,
      "text": "This long-time carwash is now owned and operated by its 20 workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 461340.0,
      "end_time": 463364.0,
      "text": "all of whom are union members as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 463388.0,
      "end_time": 468623.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 468648.0,
      "end_time": 472546.0,
      "text": "So you might be wondering why the focus on union-worker ownership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 472570.0,
      "end_time": 474197.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a lot of good reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 474221.0,
      "end_time": 477971.0,
      "text": "why the labor movement is a natural ally to the worker-ownership movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 477995.0,
      "end_time": 480591.0,
      "text": "To build these companies that we want in our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 480615.0,
      "end_time": 481766.0,
      "text": "we need a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 481790.0,
      "end_time": 484388.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to need money, people and training."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 484820.0,
      "end_time": 486599.0,
      "text": "Unions have all of those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 487700.0,
      "end_time": 490667.0,
      "text": "America&#39;s working class has been paying union dues for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 490691.0,
      "end_time": 492739.0,
      "text": "and with it, our unions have been building"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 492763.0,
      "end_time": 495597.0,
      "text": "dignified, decent, and democratic workplaces for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 495621.0,
      "end_time": 498460.0,
      "text": "However, union jobs are on the steep decline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 498700.0,
      "end_time": 500476.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s time for us to start calling on our unions"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 500500.0,
      "end_time": 504165.0,
      "text": "to really bring all of their financial and political capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 504189.0,
      "end_time": 507872.0,
      "text": "to bear in the creation of new, union, living-wage jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 507896.0,
      "end_time": 509109.0,
      "text": "in our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 509693.0,
      "end_time": 512924.0,
      "text": "Also, union halls are full of union members"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 512948.0,
      "end_time": 516910.0,
      "text": "who understand the importance of solidarity"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 516115.0,
      "end_time": 518236.0,
      "text": "and the power of collective action."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 519148.0,
      "end_time": 523577.0,
      "text": "These are the types of folks that want more union businesses to exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 523601.0,
      "end_time": 525811.0,
      "text": "so let&#39;s build them with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 527670.0,
      "end_time": 528330.0,
      "text": "Learning from our unions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 528354.0,
      "end_time": 529505.0,
      "text": "learning from our past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 529529.0,
      "end_time": 530702.0,
      "text": "learning from our peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 530726.0,
      "end_time": 533370.0,
      "text": "are all going to be very important to our success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 533394.0,
      "end_time": 536298.0,
      "text": "which is why I&#39;d like to leave you with one last example"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 536322.0,
      "end_time": 538346.0,
      "text": "and a vision for the future ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 538973.0,
      "end_time": 541800.0,
      "text": "and that vision is Mondragon, Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 542305.0,
      "end_time": 547110.0,
      "text": "Mondragon, Spain is a community built entirely around worker cooperatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 547521.0,
      "end_time": 550482.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s 260-plus businesses here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 550506.0,
      "end_time": 555283.0,
      "text": "manufacturing everything from bicycles to washing machines to transformers."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 555866.0,
      "end_time": 559382.0,
      "text": "And this group of businesses now employs 80,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 559406.0,
      "end_time": 562510.0,
      "text": "and earns more than 12 billion euros in revenue every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 563241.0,
      "end_time": 567266.0,
      "text": "And all of the companies there are owned by the people that work in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 567716.0,
      "end_time": 572432.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve also built universities and hospitals and financial institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 572456.0,
      "end_time": 576325.0,
      "text": "I mean, imagine if we could build something like this in South-Central."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 577659.0,
      "end_time": 580934.0,
      "text": "The late mayor of Jackson had a similar idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 581385.0,
      "end_time": 586813.0,
      "text": "He wanted to turn his entire city into a Mondragon-like cooperative economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 586837.0,
      "end_time": 589746.0,
      "text": "calling his ambitious plan \"Jackson Rising.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 590760.0,
      "end_time": 592186.0,
      "text": "And when I look at Mondragon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 592210.0,
      "end_time": 595200.0,
      "text": "I see really what working-class people can do for ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 595440.0,
      "end_time": 596194.0,
      "text": "when we work together"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 596219.0,
      "end_time": 598775.0,
      "text": "and make decisions for ourselves and each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 598799.0,
      "end_time": 600107.0,
      "text": "and our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 603336.0,
      "end_time": 606315.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s really incredible about Mondragon"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 606339.0,
      "end_time": 608806.0,
      "text": "is that while we are dreaming about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 608830.0,
      "end_time": 610751.0,
      "text": "they are dreaming about us."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 611285.0,
      "end_time": 616145.0,
      "text": "This community in Spain has decided to launch an international initiative"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 616169.0,
      "end_time": 619170.0,
      "text": "to create more communities like it all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 619195.0,
      "end_time": 620802.0,
      "text": "by linking up with unions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 620826.0,
      "end_time": 622739.0,
      "text": "by supporting organizations like LUCI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 622763.0,
      "end_time": 625661.0,
      "text": "and by educating folks about the worker-ownership model."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 627177.0,
      "end_time": 629692.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s what you can do to be a part of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 629716.0,
      "end_time": 632296.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a union member, go to your union meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 632320.0,
      "end_time": 635510.0,
      "text": "and make sure that your union has a worker-ownership initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 635534.0,
      "end_time": 636684.0,
      "text": "and become a part of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 637177.0,
      "end_time": 638451.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re an entrepreneur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 638475.0,
      "end_time": 639895.0,
      "text": "if you have a small business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 639919.0,
      "end_time": 641738.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re interested in starting one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 641762.0,
      "end_time": 644429.0,
      "text": "then link up with LUCI or another organization like us"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 644453.0,
      "end_time": 646747.0,
      "text": "to help you get started on the cooperative model."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 647780.0,
      "end_time": 648230.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a politician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 648254.0,
      "end_time": 649646.0,
      "text": "or you work for one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 649670.0,
      "end_time": 651337.0,
      "text": "or you just like talking to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 651361.0,
      "end_time": 655598.0,
      "text": "please get the city, state, federal and county legislation passed"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 655622.0,
      "end_time": 659113.0,
      "text": "that we need in order to fund and support worker-owned businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 659807.0,
      "end_time": 661400.0,
      "text": "And for everybody else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 661640.0,
      "end_time": 663303.0,
      "text": "learn about our history, learn about our models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 663327.0,
      "end_time": 664953.0,
      "text": "and seek us out so can support us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 664977.0,
      "end_time": 668184.0,
      "text": "you can buy from us, invest in us, lend to us and join us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 668208.0,
      "end_time": 670274.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s really going to take all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 670298.0,
      "end_time": 673918.0,
      "text": "in order to build the more just and sustainable and resilient economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 673942.0,
      "end_time": 676873.0,
      "text": "that we want for ourselves and our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 677679.0,
      "end_time": 678908.0,
      "text": "And with that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 678932.0,
      "end_time": 682123.0,
      "text": "I would like to leave you with a quote from Arundhati Roy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 682147.0,
      "end_time": 683297.0,
      "text": "and she writes ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 684367.0,
      "end_time": 688517.0,
      "text": "\"Our strategy should not be only to confront Empire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 688542.0,
      "end_time": 690160.0,
      "text": "but to lay siege to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 691160.0,
      "end_time": 692611.0,
      "text": "To deprive it of oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 693549.0,
      "end_time": 694915.0,
      "text": "To mock it."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 694939.0,
      "end_time": 696890.0,
      "text": "To shame it."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 696701.0,
      "end_time": 697916.0,
      "text": "With our art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 697940.0,
      "end_time": 699114.0,
      "text": "our literature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 699138.0,
      "end_time": 700402.0,
      "text": "our music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 700426.0,
      "end_time": 701576.0,
      "text": "our brilliance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 702131.0,
      "end_time": 703281.0,
      "text": "our joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 703973.0,
      "end_time": 705718.0,
      "text": "our sheer relentlessness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 706394.0,
      "end_time": 708528.0,
      "text": "and our ability to tell our own stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 709260.0,
      "end_time": 711756.0,
      "text": "Not the stories that we&#39;re being brainwashed to believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 713549.0,
      "end_time": 715617.0,
      "text": "The corporate revolution will collapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 715642.0,
      "end_time": 717872.0,
      "text": "if we refuse to buy what they&#39;re selling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 719560.0,
      "end_time": 720206.0,
      "text": "their ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 720539.0,
      "end_time": 722146.0,
      "text": "their version of history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 722171.0,
      "end_time": 723322.0,
      "text": "their wars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 723346.0,
      "end_time": 724515.0,
      "text": "their weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 725144.0,
      "end_time": 726578.0,
      "text": "their sense of inevitability."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 727776.0,
      "end_time": 728925.0,
      "text": "Because know this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 729624.0,
      "end_time": 731502.0,
      "text": "They be few and we be many."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 732530.0,
      "end_time": 733939.0,
      "text": "They need us more than we need them."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 734956.0,
      "end_time": 737122.0,
      "text": "Another world is not only possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 737542.0,
      "end_time": 738692.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s on her way."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 739477.0,
      "end_time": 740669.0,
      "text": "And on a quiet day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 741272.0,
      "end_time": 742613.0,
      "text": "I can hear her breathing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 743148.0,
      "end_time": 744299.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 744323.0,
      "end_time": 746223.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}